            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[全力以赴]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d9/2023_fighting_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>积极调节心情！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E7%B4%A7%E5%BC%A0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E7%B4%A7%E5%BC%A0%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长期精神高度紧张增加胃癌风险#</span></a>】医生表示，胃病多是“精神病”。当人出现愤怒、焦虑、抑郁等不良情绪时，机体就会不可避免地经历一次“炎症风暴”。长期处于精神高度紧张状态，会增加罹患胃癌的风险。因此，面对不良情绪一定要选择积极的方式进行调节👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WZ8l1Y" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
