            <title><![CDATA[想缓解便秘，你得吃熟香蕉[doge]🍌不少人觉得吃香蕉可以缓解便秘，[话筒]卫子提醒，想通过吃香蕉补充膳食纤维缓解便秘，需要吃8-10根，甚至更多！重点是，还得...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[想缓解便秘，你得吃熟香蕉<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>🍌<br><br>不少人觉得吃香蕉可以缓解便秘，<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子提醒，想通过吃香蕉补充膳食纤维缓解便秘，需要吃8-10根，甚至更多！重点是，还得是熟香蕉。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>因为不太成熟的香蕉中含有一定的鞣(róu)酸和抗性淀粉，二者结合后吸干粪便中的水分，反而可能会造成便秘。（emm，你卫也吃错好多年<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[摊手]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_tanshou-fa05d4eacf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[闭嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bizui-3381378bab.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisn606pp1j20n30ra761.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
